---
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section section--tint af-s5">
  <div class="container--narrow">

    <h2 class="af-s5__heading">
      What To Expect During Your 70-Minute Acne Facial Experience
    </h2>

    <p class="af-s5__intro">
      Each session is customized to your skin's unique needs, combining the most advanced Korean skincare techniques with medical-grade ingredients for maximum results.
    </p>

    <ol class="af-s5__steps">

      <li class="af-s5__step">
        <div class="af-s5__step-num" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
        <div class="af-s5__step-body">
          <h3 class="af-s5__step-title">Deep Pore Cleansing</h3>
          <p class="af-s5__step-desc">
            We begin with a thorough double cleanse using medical-grade formulas to remove makeup, sunscreen, and surface impurities, preparing your skin to fully absorb the active treatment ingredients.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="af-s5__step">
        <div class="af-s5__step-num" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
        <div class="af-s5__step-body">
          <h3 class="af-s5__step-title">Exfoliation &amp; Pore Extraction</h3>
          <p class="af-s5__step-desc">
            Gentle enzymatic exfoliation removes dead skin cells while manual extractions clear blackheads and congested pores safely, reducing the risk of scarring and post-inflammatory hyperpigmentation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="af-s5__step">
        <div class="af-s5__step-num" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
        <div class="af-s5__step-body">
          <h3 class="af-s5__step-title">Medical-Grade Active Treatment</h3>
          <p class="af-s5__step-desc">
            A targeted serum blend of Salicylic Acid, Tea Tree, and anti-inflammatory botanicals is applied to penetrate deeply, killing acne-causing bacteria and calming active breakouts at the source.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="af-s5__step">
        <div class="af-s5__step-num" aria-hidden="true">4</div>
        <div class="af-s5__step-body">
          <h3 class="af-s5__step-title">Soothing &amp; Healing Mask</h3>
          <p class="af-s5__step-desc">
            A customized hydrogel or clay mask draws out remaining impurities while delivering Centella Asiatica and calming actives to reduce redness, soothe irritation, and begin the healing process.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="af-s5__step">
        <div class="af-s5__step-num" aria-hidden="true">5</div>
        <div class="af-s5__step-body">
          <h3 class="af-s5__step-title">Barrier Repair &amp; Sun Protection</h3>
          <p class="af-s5__step-desc">
            We finish with a lightweight moisturizer and broad-spectrum SPF to lock in results, protect freshly treated skin, and keep your skin barrier strong between sessions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>

    </ol>

    <div class="af-s5__cta">
      <a
        href={site.calcomUrl}
        class="btn btn--primary btn--lg"
      >
        Schedule Now
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .af-s5__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .af-s5__intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .af-s5__steps {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .af-s5__step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .af-s5__step-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-cta);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .af-s5__step-body {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .af-s5__step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .af-s5__step-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .af-s5__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .af-s5__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
